### Smart Agriculture API — sample requests (use with REST Client / Postman)
### Base URL: http://localhost:8080

### Register (FARMER only when app.security.allow-only-farmer-self-registration=true)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fullName": "Ravi Kumar",
  "email": "ravi@example.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "phoneNumber": "+91 9876543210",
  "role": "FARMER"
}

### Login
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "ravi@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Create farmer (FARMER: omit userId; ADMIN: set userId)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/farmers
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "userId": null,
  "farmerName": "Ravi Kumar",
  "village": "Nelamangala",
  "district": "Bangalore Rural",
  "state": "Karnataka",
  "landArea": 12.5,
  "soilType": "Red loam"
}

### Add crop
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/crops
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "farmerId": 1,
  "cropName": "Tomato",
  "cropType": "Vegetable",
  "sowingDate": "2026-03-01",
  "harvestingDate": null,
  "cropStatus": "GROWING"
}

### Sensor data
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/sensor-data
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "farmerId": 1,
  "temperature": 28.5,
  "humidity": 62.0,
  "soilMoisture": 35.0
}

### Start irrigation (optional body)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/irrigation/farmers/1/start
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "waterLevel": 75.0
}

### Weather current (Open-Meteo)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/weather/current?latitude=12.97&longitude=77.59
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Save weather snapshot
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/weather/save
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "latitude": 12.97,
  "longitude": 77.59,
  "farmerId": 1
}

### Notification send
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/notifications/send
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "farmerId": 1,
  "title": "Reminder",
  "message": "Inspect drip lines in block A.",
  "notificationType": "GENERAL"
}

### Low soil moisture alert
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/notifications/alerts/low-soil-moisture
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "farmerId": 1,
  "soilMoisture": 18.0,
  "threshold": 25.0
}
